OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1783678766
OL,3,CSouth East Water launches dedicated
OL,4,Csupport for livestock owners during
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FSouth East Water has launched a new
OL,8,Femergency support system to protect
OL,9,Flivestock during unplanned water
OL,10,Foutages.
OL,12,FThe company, which covers parts of
OL,13,FHampshire, Berkshire, Surrey, Sussex
OL,14,Fand Kent, says it will give farmers in
OL,15,Fits supply area a vital safety net.
OL,17,FThey say the new framework outlines a
OL,18,Frapid, structured deployment of
OL,19,Femergency water supplies specifically
OL,20,Ftailored to the needs of local
OL,21,Flivestock handlers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
