OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1783678766
OL,3,CSouth East Water launches dedicated
OL,4,Csupport for livestock owners during
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FThe supplier recently appointed new
OL,8,Fincoming chief executive John Halsall
OL,9,Fafter its former boss announced plans
OL,10,Fto step down in the wake of major
OL,11,Fsupply outages in Kent and Sussex.
OL,13,FThousands of customers were left
OL,14,Funable to access tap water, shower or
OL,15,Fflush their toilets during the outages
OL,16,Fbetween November and January.
OL,18,FAnd there have been repeated outages
OL,19,Facross Kent and Sussex since then,
OL,20,Fwith tens of thousands left with water
OL,21,Fsupply issues again in May and June.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1783678766
OL,3,CSouth East Water launches dedicated
OL,4,Csupport for livestock owners during
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FThe water company says the livestock
OL,8,Fregister has been developed following
OL,9,Flessons learned from previous water
OL,10,Fsupply interruptions and feedback from
OL,11,Flivestock owners that water outages
OL,12,Fpose an immediate threat to animal
OL,13,Fwelfare and farm livelihoods.
OL,15,FThe company say the plan ensures that
OL,16,Fcritical support is on the ground
OL,17,Fwithin 48 hours of an outage, with
OL,18,Femergency teams prioritising areas
OL,19,Ffacing the highest animal welfare
OL,20,Frisks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1783678766
OL,3,CSouth East Water launches dedicated
OL,4,Csupport for livestock owners during
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FFor livestock owners who have six or
OL,8,Fmore animals, the drinking water
OL,9,Fcompany will deliver direct water
OL,10,Fsupport tailored to the setup of the
OL,11,Ffarm.
OL,13,FDepending on the individual needs, the
OL,14,Fbusiness will use reasonable
OL,15,Fendeavours to provide water through
OL,16,Feither emergency bottled water for
OL,17,Fyoung or vulnerable stock, mobile
OL,18,Fbowsers, strategically placed static
OL,19,Ftanks, and direct bulk tanker
OL,20,Fdeliveries straight into on-farm
OL,21,Fstorage tanks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1783678766
OL,3,CSouth East Water launches dedicated
OL,4,Csupport for livestock owners during
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FFor smallholders, with five or fewer
OL,8,Fanimals, during a water outage, the
OL,9,Fdrinking water company will set up
OL,10,Ffilling points as close to the
OL,11,Faffected area as possible to provide
OL,12,Fquick, easy access to bulk and bottled
OL,13,Fwater for self-collection. This
OL,14,Fenables smallholders to easily fill
OL,15,Fstorage units such as water bowsers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1783678766
OL,3,CSouth East Water launches dedicated
OL,4,Csupport for livestock owners during
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FDouglas Whitfield, Water Supply
OL,8,FDirector at South East Water, said:
OL,9,F"We know we need to make improvements
OL,10,Fand we're committed to doing things
OL,11,Fbetter. We recognise that disruptions
OL,12,Fto the water supply present a direct
OL,13,Fthreat to livestock welfare and
OL,14,Fagricultural livelihoods
OL,16,F"Following lessons learned and
OL,17,Ffeedback from previous incidents, this
OL,18,Fnew approach gives our local farming
OL,19,Fcommunity the support they need when
OL,20,Funexpected disruptions happen."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1783678766
OL,3,CSouth East Water launches dedicated
OL,4,Csupport for livestock owners during
OL,5,Coutages
OL,7,FAlthough South East Water is providing
OL,8,Fthis emergency support, it is still
OL,9,Fencouraging anyone with livestock to
OL,10,Fhave their own contingency plans in
OL,11,Fplace, such as on-farm water storage.
OL,13,FLivestock owners in South East Water's
OL,14,Fsupply areas, from commercial farms to
OL,15,Fprivate smallholders, are encouraged
OL,16,Fto register their details online via
OL,17,FSouth East Water's website.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
